            <a name="del_another"></a>
            <h3 class="title">3. DELIVERY TO ANOTHER CITY</h3>
            <div class="anchor_text_text">
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>Delivery by Russian Post or SDEK is available to any location in Russia.</p>
                    <p>The cost depends on the delivery location and the weight of the parcel.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>You can find out the exact shipping cost in your shopping cart. To do this, add the necessary products to your cart, open the cart, 
                        and indicate your city in the appropriate field of the form. In a couple of seconds, several options for delivering the parcel to your city
                        will be displayed.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
