            <h3 class="title">4. RETERN</h3>
            <div class="anchor_text_text">
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>Despite reliable packaging and cooperation with the best transport companies, there are cases when:</p>
                </div>
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>— 1. Gummies arrive melted due to non-compliance with the temperature during transportation</p>
                    <p>— 2. The seal is broken or the packaging is severely damaged</p>
                </div>
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>Unfortunately, during the transportation process we cannot influence this, so we provide the opportunity for partial
                        or a full refund. In the first case we will refund the full cost of the order, in the second we will return the cost of the order
                        minus shipping costs. In other cases, the problem is solved individually.</p>
                </div>
