            <div class="anchor_text_text anchor_text_text_bottom">
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>To receive a refund:</p>
                </div>
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>— 1. Take a photo of the contents of the parcel and the mailbox</p>
                    <p>— 2. Send an email to <a class="href_green" href="#">mail@mail.com</a>, briefly describing the problem, attaching photographs of the parcel and indicating bank details for a refund (a bank card number is sufficient)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>You will receive a confirmation email within 24 hours.</p>
                    <p>Within 12 hours after confirmation, we will return the funds to the bank account you specified.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="anchor_paragraph">
                    <p>Such situations happen extremely rarely, so in addition to the return <a class="href_green" href="#">you will receive an individual promotional code</a> for extra gummies on your next order :)</p>
